## AUTOMATED LOCAL GIT INSTALL

### Local `git` install and setup:

```
cd piranha-master/ ;
cd install/ ;
chmod u+x ./* ;
local_piranha ;
#
cp local_piranha ~/bin/ ; # makes installer available from command line, for future use (assuming ~/bin/ is in $PATH, as usual)
```

## AUTOMATED HOMEBREW INSTALL

### `brew` install and setup:

```
cd piranha-master/ ;
cd install/ ;
chmod u+x ./* ;
brew_piranha ;
#
cp brew_piranha ~/bin/ ; # makes installer available from command line, for future use (assuming ~/bin/ is in $PATH, as usual)
```

For information on options for installing 'by-hand', please see the Quick Guide for the Impatient 
(https://github.com/justincbagley/piranha/wiki#quick-guide-for-the-impatient) in the PIrANHA
GitHub Wiki pages (https://github.com/justincbagley/piranha/wiki).
